y of human vulnerability and the limits of empathy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aArt, Moderny21st century. 0aDwellings in art. 0aDwellingsxSocial aspects. 7aART / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311127365508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311066594940uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/9781487514679zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487514679zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781487514679/original  a978-3-11-066594-9 University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-127365-5 ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA